title: 1961–62 Midland Football League
text:
The 1961–62 Midland Football League season was the 62nd in the history of the <a href="Midland%20Football%20League%20%281889%29">Midland Football League</a>, a <a href="association%20football">football</a> competition in <a href="England">England</a>.
Due to financial problems the league folded and no matches were played in the previous season.
Clubs.
The league featured six clubs which competed in the previous season, along with twelve new clubs.
